seqid

Source: R/seqid.R
seqid.Rd

This function returns the first whitespace separated names value of a XStringSet.

seqid(x)

Arguments

x

XStringSet [mandatory]

Value

chr

Author

Kristian K Ullrich

Examples

##load example sequence data
data("ath", package="CRBHits")
seqid(ath)
